thread.title: BRIEF-Vanc Pharmaceuticals Enters Into Supply And Distribution Agreement With Affiliate Of Emerald Health Therapeutics

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Vanc Pharmaceuticals Enters Into Supply And Distribution Agreement With Affiliate Of Emerald Health Therapeutics
text:
April 17, 2018 / 8:08 AM / Updated 14 minutes ago BRIEF-Vanc Pharmaceuticals Enters Into Supply And Distribution Agreement With Affiliate Of Emerald Health Therapeutics Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 17 (Reuters) - Emerald Health Therapeutics Inc : 
* VANC PHARMACEUTICALS SAYS HAS ENTERED INTO A SUPPLY AND DISTRIBUTION AGREEMENT WITH AN AFFILIATE OF EMERALD HEALTH THERAPEUTICS, INC 
* WAS GRANTED RIGHTS TO SELL AND DISTRIBUTE CERTAIN PROPRIETARY ENDOCANNABINOID-SUPPORTING PRODUCTS IN CANADA TO LICENSED PHARMACIES 
* CONCURRENT WITH EXECUTION OF AGREEMENTS, VANC ISSUED TO EMERALDâ€™S AFFILIATE WARRANTS TO BUY 3.03 MILLION SHARES AT $0.33/SHARE FOR 24 MONTHS Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
